OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FEditors fear police        
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fguidance on links with     
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fjournalists                
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Editors have questioned police guidance
OL,6, which they say links journalists with  
OL,7, corruption, and "equates them with the 
OL,8, wrongdoing they work to uncover".      
OL,10,FNational College of Policing guidelines
OL,11,Fsay officers should declare            
OL,12,Frelationships with journalists, just as
OL,13,Fthey have to with convicted criminals. 
OL,15,FBut the Society of Editors says        
OL,16,Fjournalists should not be included on a
OL,17,Flist of "notifiable associations".     
OL,19,FThe guidelines only came to light      
OL,20,Fearlier this year.                     
